original_body_lines: Madhushan Chandrajith of the University of Peradeniya has been elected as the new Convenor of the Inter-University Students’ Federation (IUSF).
Issuing a statement, the previous Convenor of the IUSF Wasantha Mudalige stated that the new appointment was made during the IUSF meeting held at the Rajarata University, yesterday (May 20).
